author: ajaypaibir
msg: Added support for inout, out variables. Fixed a bug in inferring operation name at Reader, some bugs related to inout, out variables  while wrapping primitive types.
Added unit tests for the above bug fixes.
Enabled SOAP TypeTest for primitive types.
Note xsd:date issue around marshalling of uninitialized date object is still pending. Will be addressed in next merge.

author: adisakala
msg: Fixed wsdl2java.bat issue with quotes around arguments.

author: cjodea
msg: update JAXWS RI veresion to nightly build of 2005-11-09
Fixed minor problem with JAXBEncoderDecoderTest when unmarshalling XML without namespace set
updated ResourceInjector to call PostConstruct annotated methods
Added support for @Resources annotation in ResourceInjector

author: andreasmyth
msg: Extension of Spring XML schema to support arbitrary data types.
Extended schema allows ANY child elements as well as text for the value element and thus is upward compatible.
Implemented custom xml bean factory, parser as well as JAXB based property editors to handle schema extension.
